totalInetBytesSent.name: totalInetBytesSent
totalInetBytesSent.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy service to remote servers on the Internet, or to a chained upstream proxy.

totalInetBytesRecvd.name: totalInetBytesRecvd
totalInetBytesRecvd.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy service from remote servers on the Internet, or from a chained upstream proxy, in response to requests from the Web Proxy service.

totalInetBytes.name: totalInetBytes
totalInetBytes.description: The total rate for all bytes transferred between ISA Server and remote servers on the Internet, or a chained upstream proxy.

totalClntBytesSent.name: totalClntBytesSent
totalClntBytesSent.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy service to Web Proxy clients.

totalClntBytesRecvd.name: totalClntBytesRecvd
totalClntBytesRecvd.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy service from Web Proxy clients.

totalClntBytes.name: totalClntBytes
totalClntBytes.description: The sum of Client Bytes Sent/sec and Client Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the Web Proxy service and Web Proxy clients.

totalSSLClntBytesSent.name: totalSSLClntBytesSent
totalSSLClntBytesSent.description: The rate at which Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy service to secured Web Proxy clients.

totalSSLClntBytesRecvd.name: totalSSLClntBytesRecvd
totalSSLClntBytesRecvd.description: The rate at which Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) data bytes are received by the Web Proxy service from secured Web Proxy clients.

totalSSLClntBytes.name: totalSSLClntBytes
totalSSLClntBytes.description: The sum of SSL Client Bytes Sent/sec and Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the Web Proxy service and secured Web Proxy clients.

currentUsers.name: currentUsers
currentUsers.description: The number of users currently connected to the Web Proxy service.

totalUsers.name: totalUsers
totalUsers.description: The total number of users that have ever connected to the Web Proxy service.

maxUsers.name: maxUsers
maxUsers.description: The maximum number of users that have connected to the Web Proxy service simultaneously.

ftpRequests.name: ftpRequests
ftpRequests.description: The number of Ftp requests that have been made to the Web Proxy service.

gopherRequests.name: gopherRequests
gopherRequests.description: The number of Gopher requests that have been made to the Web Proxy service.

httpRequests.name: httpRequests
httpRequests.description: The number of Http requests that have been made to the Web Proxy service.

totalRequests.name: totalRequests
totalRequests.description: The total number of requests that have ever been made to the Web Proxy service.

totalSuccRequests.name: totalSuccRequests
totalSuccRequests.description: The total number of requests that have been successfully processed by the Web Proxy service.

totalFailRequests.name: totalFailRequests
totalFailRequests.description: The total number of requests that have failed to be processed due to errors. Errors can be the result of the Web Proxy service failing to locate a requested server URL on the Internet or because of the Web Proxy client being denied access to the requested URL.

totalCacheFetches.name: totalCacheFetches
totalCacheFetches.description: The total number of Web Proxy client requests that have been served by using data from the ISA Server cache.

totalInetFetches.name: totalInetFetches
totalInetFetches.description: The total number of requests that have been served by using data retrieved from remote servers on the Internet or from a chained upstream ISA Server computer.

cacheHitRatio.name: cacheHitRatio
cacheHitRatio.description: The percentage of Web Proxy client requests that have been served using cached data, out of the total number of Web Proxy client requests to the ISA Server.

cacheRunningHitRatio.name: cacheRunningHitRatio
cacheRunningHitRatio.description: The percentage of Web Proxy client requests that have been served using cached data out of the total number of Web Proxy client requests to the ISA Server, for the last 10,000 requests serviced.

totalSitesDenied.name: totalSitesDenied
totalSitesDenied.description: The total number of Internet sites to which the Web Proxy service has denied access.

totalSitesGranted.name: totalSitesGranted
totalSitesGranted.description: The total number of Internet sites to which the Web Proxy service has granted access.

dnsCacheEntries.name: dnsCacheEntries
dnsCacheEntries.description: The current number of DNS domain name entries cached as a result of Web Proxy service activity.

dnsCacheRetrievals.name: dnsCacheRetrievals
dnsCacheRetrievals.description: The total number of DNS domain names that have been retrieved by the Web Proxy service.

dnsCacheFlushes.name: dnsCacheFlushes
dnsCacheFlushes.description: The total number of times that the DNS domain name cache has been flushed or cleared by the Web Proxy service.

dnsCacheHits.name: dnsCacheHits
dnsCacheHits.description: The total number of times a DNS domain name was found within the DNS Cache by the Web Proxy service.

dnsCacheRatio.name: dnsCacheRatio
dnsCacheRatio.description: The percentage of DNS domain names served by the DNS cache, out of a total of all DNS entries that have been retrieved by the Web Proxy service.

httpsSessions.name: httpsSessions
httpsSessions.description: The total number of HTTP-secured sessions serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) tunnel.

snewsSessions.name: snewsSessions
snewsSessions.description: The total number of SNEWS sessions serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) tunnel.

sslSessions.name: sslSessions
sslSessions.description: The total number of unknown Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) sessions serviced by the SSL tunnel.

sslTotalSessions.name: sslTotalSessions
sslTotalSessions.description: The total number of Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) sessions serviced by the SSL tunnel.

threadPoolSize.name: threadPoolSize
threadPoolSize.description: The number of threads in the thread pool.

threadPoolFailures.name: threadPoolFailures
threadPoolFailures.description: The number of requests rejected because the thread pool was overcommitted.

poolSessions.name: poolSessions
poolSessions.description: The number of sessions being actively serviced by thread pool threads.

totalArrayBytesSent.name: totalArrayBytesSent
totalArrayBytesSent.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the ISA Server to other servers within the same array.

totalArrayBytesRecvd.name: totalArrayBytesRecvd
totalArrayBytesRecvd.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the ISA Server from other servers within the same array in response to requests from the Web Proxy service.

totalArrayBytes.name: totalArrayBytes
totalArrayBytes.description: The sum of Array Bytes Sent/sec and Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the ISA Server and other members of the same array.

totalProcessingTime.name: totalProcessingTime
totalProcessingTime.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).

totalArrayFetches.name: totalArrayFetches
totalArrayFetches.description: The total number of Web Proxy client requests that have been serviced by requesting the data from another ISA Server within the array.

totalReverseBytesSent.name: totalReverseBytesSent
totalReverseBytesSent.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy service to Web publishing servers in response to incoming Web requests.

totalReverseBytesRecvd.name: totalReverseBytesRecvd
totalReverseBytesRecvd.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy service from Web publishing servers in response to incoming Web requests.

totalReverseBytes.name: totalReverseBytes
totalReverseBytes.description: The sum of Reverse Bytes Sent/sec and Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the ISA Server and Web publishing servers in response to incoming Web requests.

totalReverseFetches.name: totalReverseFetches
totalReverseFetches.description: The total number of incoming Web requests that have been serviced by using data retrieved from Web publishing servers.

totalPendingConnects.name: totalPendingConnects
totalPendingConnects.description: The total number of pending connects.

totalMemberProcessingTime.name: totalMemberProcessingTime
totalMemberProcessingTime.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request that is fetched through another array member (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).

totalDirectProcessingTime.name: totalDirectProcessingTime
totalDirectProcessingTime.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request directly to the Web server or Upstream proxy (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).

totalCacheProcessingTime.name: totalCacheProcessingTime
totalCacheProcessingTime.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request from cache (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).
